Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
What does it mean to have a relationship？
What's with that kind of question？
You see, I've changed since we started dating, but I wonder how you see me now. It feels like I'm the only one who worries.
You're still you. I don't think you've changed at all ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Huh？
You've been so kind and beautiful, ever since the first time I met you.
...You're so unfair. ...But, thank you. It's better than being told that I've changed.
I see, then what do you think about me？
Do you want me to say it？ You have not changed. You're still so nice.
Even though you can hear me... Oh, I don't know anymore.
(I wanted to hear you say it again.)
Manaka
You know, I was talking with a friend before, right？ We were talking about what does it mean to have a relationship？
What do you mean？ ...Hmm？
Everyone was making sounds like they were disgusted. It's hard to put into words.
I think I might know why. So, did you get your answer？
Yes. It's my own answer, though. It's to be the closest to the one you like.
I can be closer to you than anyone else. That kind of thing is what I believe.
... Then, everyone was laughing at me.
Eh！ Did you tell that to everyone？
Yes. But you know, I wish you could forget what I told you about now...
(I can't do that...)
What do you think it means to be dating？
Manaka
What's wrong with your face？ Alright, I'll think about the meaning with you.
Hmm... It could be like never letting you go？
I see, then we can monopolize each other.
Who knows, do you think that's true？
Emm, it's not that！？
...I'm kidding.
Manaka will always be yours▼
(Yes, I'll never let you go...)
What do girls usually have on their minds？
Manaka
What's wrong？ That was too sudden.
I'm a little curious about it.
Hehe... What about boys？
That is, well...
... Pervert.
Huh！？ I didn't say anything！
I'm kidding. Why did you panic that much？
(I didn't know you could tease someone ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Do you know what girls have on their minds？
Manaka
What's wrong？ What... Did something happened？
There was a girl from my class who started crying the other day.
Do you know if she was sad...？
I do wonder. Maybe she had a lack of sleep or was too nervous... I don't know.
Oh, I see... But, I'm a little worried.
I'm worried about that too. And I was wondering if such things happen to you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Me？ I'm probably fine. Even if... if I suddenly feel sad sometimes... you know？
Huh？ What do you mean？
Hmm？
...Yup！ I think it's okay after all.
(Huh？ What's that mean？？)
What do girls usually think？
Manaka
Girls？ Not me？ Is there another girl you care about？
No！ It's not like that！
...Hehe！
I'm sorry. I'm just thinking about you so much and I said something like that.
To answer your question... Are you alright？
Of course！
▲高嶺＊＊▲？ Your face is red, are you okay？
Manaka
Yes, my heart is beating so fast.
It might be a fever... Let me touch your forehead---
Kyaa！
What's wrong？
It's because you're the one who makes my heart beat.
Did I do something wrong？
No. Sometimes when I think of you... This is what happens.
Usually, it's when I'm alone. Sometimes when I look at my face... Hey, how can I fix it？
(I want to help you, but I don't wish for that...)
Hey, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. When do you feel nervous？
Manaka
Nervous？ Well...
When you and I meet at school... I wonder.
With me？
Yes. When I see you in the distance and then you notice me. That's when our eyes lock, right？
I was truly happy when that happened... After that you laughed a little... I really liked that.
Huh？
...And I just went and told you that. Please just forget about it, okay？
(Hey now, that's too much to ask！)
Manaka
Hey, do you know what the suspension bridge effect is？
If I recall correctly, it's when the brain misunderstands between the fear of crossing a suspension bridge and love.
Right. But I wonder if love is so simple that you could fall in love with someone based on that.
It would be a bit disappointing if it's true.
Yes, I'd be disappointed too. I want love to be more sacred.
When I first saw you, my heart was beating fast, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
... Really？
Of course. How about you ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
It's more than just the first time...
Huh？
Even now, when I see you, I suddenly feel nervous. I want romance to be such a wonderful thing...
Manaka
Don't you feel like time feels short when we're together？
Yeah, that's something I constantly feel.
Yes, so I was thinking about it. About the reason.
As expected from you！ Tell me why, please, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Elementary, dear Watson-kun. Perhaps it's because I'm so excited when we're together.
The heartbeat means having a high heart rate. And time flows faster than usual when it's just the two of us.
That's an interesting hypothesis.
Therefore, feeling that time is short means we're both excited... That's why we get along nicely, right？
And now there's no point in feeling time is shorter. I'm disappointed.
Manaka
*Phew*
What's wrong？
No, it's nothing. I'm alright. But... your smell...
Emm, my smell？
Yes. When I was with you, I suddenly became conscious of you smell, and I got nervous...
You always smells good. But... What about me ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I like your smell.
Well, then it's okay. Here, you can smell me！
Geez！ Don't make it sound like people are just dogs.
Haha, sorry, sorry.
Huh？ When you surprised me that way, it seems like I stopped feeling nervous.
(...Similar to hiccups.)
Manaka
You know, I was really nervous the other day.
Oh, what happened？
You were talking to another girl.
Eh！？ Really？
And it looked like you were having fun...
It's a misunderstanding！
I know, I'm just a little jealous. But...
... But？
If you make me jealous too much, I might make you nervous too, okay？
That means... You get along with other guys？ ...I don't like that ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Okay.
Manaka
Did my fashion sense changed recently？
Yeah, I think so... Does that make you happy？
Yup. I haven't really thought about fashion that much... It's fresh to hear I've changed.
I see, I also liked you fashion sense when we first met, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Thank you. But you know, I really want you to see me in various ways... I'm kidding.
Hehe, so be prepared for it！
(I'm really glad you changed a little because of me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Manaka
I'm sorry for being late, I forgot my phone at home and rushed to get it back.
Haha, so you also forget things sometimes ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Don't make fun of me. So when I got it, I suddenly realized...
What？ What's wrong？
I never thought I would have do that before I started dating you.
Before we started dating ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yes. I'm sure I won't miss those days. I went back to get it, because... I'm always waiting for your messages.
I see, thank you so much.
No... I should be thanking you. It's wonderful to think I changed with only that small detail.
Hehe, so send me a lot of emails and call me a lot！ Okay？
Alright！
Manaka
Since this is the first time I've been in a relationship, I've come to understand...
What did you realize？
My whole persona seems to have gotten gentle.
Really...？ It's been quite some time, so I think that might be true, isn't it？
Thank you. People I've not seen a for long time, or my family told me the same. I didn't realize it.
You didn't notice it？
Yes, and that's the problem. Why is it only me...？
Why？
Geez, think it some more, please？
...Hmm, I give up.
Do you think it's because I talk to you about a lot of things？ So... you're the one who changed me.
You mean, because we are thinking the same things？
Yes. So I guess it's a joint work between you and me now, right？
Manaka
I've been asked for directions by random people, and even kids call me to play.
I'm sure it's because you're so reliable. And the kids want to play with their beautiful onee-san, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Even if you praise me that much, you will get nothing from it.
Haha. There are people who are easy to talk to, and you have a really gentle aura.
Is that a gift from our relationship？ And my aura... Someone told me the same once.
Huh？ Really？
One time, someone who I helped to find their way, told me that his ex's aura was coming from me.
No... that was not it！ It was a pickup line ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Really？ I thought it would be better to ask the policeman, so I took him to the police box...
(*Phew* That made me worry. I need to keep an eye on ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Manaka
Ah, I'm sorry... It's an email from Mama.
What did she say？
Yes, I'll read it out... Say hello to the person next to me. Hehe.
The person next to you... Me？
There is no one next to me, except you.
Ah yes, you're right！
Yes... Before it was "Where are you now？" Or something like that. But they've been relieved since we began dating.
I see... Then let's live up to their expectations.
Hehe. Let's continue to get along.
(I'll never let you down Takane's Mom！)
Manaka
I know it's sudden, but I have something to ask you. Is now a good time？
Yeah, what is it？
Recently, one of my friends told me that I was beautiful...
That was not a question！
Listen to me already. It's not one person, more of my friends keep telling me the same.
It feels like something began just now...
...It doesn't make sense.
Huh？ What do you mean？
Actually, I was trying to be more beautiful.
Oh, then, I think that's good. I think you achieved what you wanted.
Still, it doesn't make sense unless you notice it！
(You did this... for me？ I see...)
Manaka
Do you care too much about other couples？
...Why do you ask？
I have noticed there are things that make you look to couples around when we're on a date.
Ah, maybe I've heard something like that. Specially if we're near the same age.
I wonder if you think others couples are cute, specially if a cute girl is there.
I don't think so. I'm more worried about what you think of the man in that couple, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I think nothing about that.
That's exactly what I do！
Hehe.
Hahaha.
Yes, I don't care about other couples anymore.
(That's how it should be！)
Manaka
...Hey.
Hmm？ Do you need something？
You know...
What's wrong？
Don't you think we are kissing... too much？
Huh！？
That was the talk among my friends... That's what you do, right？ Not every date and... you said you would kiss me...
So, I'm a little worried. I think it's better not to care...
Yup！ It's better to just do our thing！
... Yes.
(I feel like I'm losing here...)
Manaka
We're better friends than any other couple, aren't we？
Oh yeah！ We fall second to none.
Hehe. That's true. You're pretty confident, aren't you？
You bet I am. That's the boyfriend power for you！
Huh？
It was something we were talking before！
Huh？ Is that so？
(It doesn't matter, I'll keep going for her！)
Manaka
I wonder how much time we've spend together.
How much time？
Yes. You know that after a year dating, we probably haven't spent half the time together, right？
You're right. At home, even during class, most of the day we're separated.
That's right. But, even if you can't be with me, I'm always thinking of you.
That's why I decided to think that even when I couldn't see you, it didn't change the fact we are dating.
Yes, rather that being together and thinking about other things, it's better to think about each other.
Yeah, that's right. Hehe, I'm glad you agree.
Me too！
Manaka
Someday, when I become an old lady, will you remember how I was？
What do you mean？
Well, you know. I was speaking about that before. You are making a bothered face, but listen to me...
I don't want to forget anything... No matter how long we've been together, no matter how small the detail...
I see. Yes, that's okay, I can remember too！
Really？
Sure, as a grandpa, I will help you remember.
...Yup！ Please do it, ▲主人公＊▲！
Leave it to me！
Manaka
Do you think we are similar？
Huh, what do you mean？
It's something one of my friends told me about. That we have a similar aura.
I wonder if that's right, I wouldn't know about that.
You're right. However, it is often said that married couples have similar auras... I was really happy to be told that.
Yes, that kind of thing sounds nice.
And you often say that dogs look like their owners, don't you？
Huh？
Yes, and you look like a cute dog.
Yes！
Shall we go for a walk？
...Woof.
